WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
Where is he now?

2
00:00:12.140 --> 00:00:13.360
Help! Help!

3
00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:15.080
Let me go!

4
00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:16.680
It’s Wu Tai!

5
00:00:18.140 --> 00:00:19.020
Wu Tai!

6
00:00:20.580 --> 00:00:21.460
Are you okay?

7
00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:23.280
It’s me! Are you hurt?

8
00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:25.300
I’ll take you to the hospital.

9
00:00:26.220 --> 00:00:26.540
I’m fine,

10
00:00:26.880 --> 00:00:28.320
they didn’t really touch me,

11
00:00:28.580 --> 00:00:29.780
just scared me a bit.

12
00:00:30.480 --> 00:00:32.520
I’m sorry, I dragged you into this.

13
00:00:32.660 --> 00:00:34.140
Lingling, don’t think like that,

14
00:00:34.140 --> 00:00:35.820
it’s not your fault,

15
00:00:35.820 --> 00:00:39.720
it’s that bastard Hou Jiuling’s fault.

16
00:00:40.300 --> 00:00:43.740
Wu Tai, let’s break up.

17
00:00:44.460 --> 00:00:45.240
No, Lingling,

18
00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:46.640
I won’t agree to break up.

19
00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:48.160
Let’s go to the police.

20
00:00:48.300 --> 00:00:49.980
Go to the police? Hou Jiuling killed

21
00:00:49.980 --> 00:00:51.380
so many people in Bangkok

22
00:00:51.380 --> 00:00:52.420
and walked away unscathed to Italy.

23
00:00:52.900 --> 00:00:54.460
Just how powerful is he?

24
00:00:54.840 --> 00:00:55.980
Can the police even catch him?

25
00:00:56.120 --> 00:00:58.100
Lingling, we can’t go to the police.

26
00:00:58.380 --> 00:01:00.240
I’m afraid if the police can’t convict him,

27
00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:00.920
then,

28
00:01:00.940 --> 00:01:02.200
he’ll come back to retaliate against us.

29
00:01:02.200 --> 00:01:03.900
Lingling, Italy isn’t actually

30
00:01:03.900 --> 00:01:04.980
as chaotic as you think.

31
00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:06.280
The police and government’s

32
00:01:06.280 --> 00:01:07.740
enforcement is quite strong.

33
00:01:08.480 --> 00:01:10.100
Today, Hou Jiuling kidnapped me,

34
00:01:10.240 --> 00:01:11.340
which is a crime in itself.

35
00:01:11.660 --> 00:01:13.020
Lingling, trust me,

36
00:01:13.120 --> 00:01:13.900
if I go testify,

37
00:01:14.120 --> 00:01:15.200
we can definitely get him convicted.